{"tid":2019641,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"京東方OLED螢幕將會在iPhone 12 上出現，是好還是壞？","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T16:14:28.000Z","uid":219147,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"94f0d10e7f4fde3c9f12db7bbd09e98a0ba76179","tid":2019641,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"最近我們已經大致上了解今年秋季 iPhone 12 系列規格和售價，其中有一個比較引起大家注意的是四款 iPhone 都會採用 OLED 螢幕，iPhone 12 Pro 系列以就是採用三星顯示(Samsung Display)的 OLED 螢幕，不過 iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Max 則是首次搭載 OLED 螢幕機種，這兩款機型則是採用中國的京東方螢幕，似乎有人不太看好這家廠商所推出的螢幕，會不會再度引起重大災情呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ufjt5pE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfjt5pE.jpg&h=cb9af793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n京東方算是中國大陸龍頭面板大廠，不過近日也傳出順利打入蘋果（iPhone 12和 iPhone 12 Max）和三星新機（Galaxy S和 Galaxy A 系列）的 OLED 螢幕供應鏈體系，甚至連同華為旗艦手機 P30Pro 就是採用東京方 AMOLED 螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n調研公司 DSCC 透過數據統計，目前全球最大的 LCD 面板供應商就是「京東方」（BOE），在手機顯示上也僅次於 LG ，是全球第三大手機 OLED 供應上，就能夠知道這家廠商在佔有率上有一定程度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4XSNDh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4XSNDh.jpg&h=279aa788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果會突然改由京東方成為新一代 iPhone 螢幕供應商，傳是蘋果為了替新 iPhone 降低成本，同時也能夠降低三星 OLED 螢幕供應依賴，也能夠將手機售價壓到 600到700美元，今年新款新機售價才能夠比 iPhone 11 售價更低，價格會來到 649 美元（約台幣23,900）。<br />\n<br />\n這也並非是單一方面來源傳出新 iPhone 12 將採用京東方螢幕，早在過去 ETNEWS 媒體就曾報告顯示，京東方已經計劃替四川的 B11 工廠OLED 工廠建立 10 條全新模組生產線，能夠將顯示面板直接連上智慧型手機，目前京東方也持續保持參與 iPhone OLED 開發項目。<br />\n<br />\n目前全球三家面板大廠中，京東方也將會在 OLED 領域分一杯羹，更會讓三星帶來極大壓力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/boe-oled-iphone-good-or-bad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fboe-oled-iphone-good-or-bad&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=5dd53678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/boe-oled-iphone-good-or-bad</a>"},{"pid":"ca885803d6cad3b769e8ba7de2e4b85e276d01dc","tid":2019641,"uid":219147,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"換句話說 除咗12 pro 係采用三星屏幕之外<br />\n其他都係支那京東oled屏募<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a1cd3d95f7795488005d8fb82ac4759113e414","tid":2019641,"uid":176282,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"港人繼續撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259b75c54371530357b969363056cd933eae2473","tid":2019641,"uid":281306,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"d1a1cd3d95f7795488005d8fb82ac4759113e414","tid":2019641,"uid":176282,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"港人繼續撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"港人會唔會撐我就唔知，我剩係知樓豬依隻5毛會繼續撐京東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUBz1D8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUBz1D8.png&h=9513170b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f69abee382879f3a919503ccde5cf0af59070fad","tid":2019641,"uid":159448,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:00:03.000Z","msg":"自己要用既野可以括免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441f3748b4bde0a6c0f5e4f2a6601d70d45ded79","tid":2019641,"uid":199957,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:01:10.000Z","msg":"之前先話要逐漸減少中國製造 結果連個mon都係京東做嘅"},{"pid":"e69d9c83f7ad1ade9efa55350e18f781b3c30829","tid":2019641,"uid":135693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f69abee382879f3a919503ccde5cf0af59070fad","tid":2019641,"uid":159448,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:00:03.000Z","msg":"自己要用既野可以括免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},